Rebbin 0.7
----------

Rebbin is an attempt to build a full featured pastebin on Ruby On Rails
to make myself learn it and learn Ruby as well.

Requirements
------------

Ruby 1.8 (developed on ruby 1.8.2 (2004-12-23) [i386-linux])
Rails 0.12.1 (developed on rails 0.12.1)
PostgreSQL 7.4 or Mysql 4 (developed on PostgreSQL 7.4.7)
Highlight 2.2-10 for utf-8 support (developed on Highlight 2.2-10)

Features
--------

see Features

License
-------

see COPYING.txt

Installation
------------

- create the db with the right config/db_schema.sql
- tune config/database.yml accordingly
- start the app with ruby script/server

